    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。时间轴我想用毫秒显示，格式设为X轴纯数字，显示用%L。另外分两个section：「Without Debounce」和「With Debounce (Infra_WorkerNode)」，这样对比清晰吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
