    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以。先画无防抖的情况：用户每输入一个字符就立即触发API调用。比如快速输入「Manila」六个字母，每个字符都在对应时间点产生milestone事件，从0ms到500ms，间隔100ms。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Type 'M' - API Call",
        "Type 'a' - API Call",
        "milestone",
        "0ms",
        "500ms"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加无防抖section，六个milestone标记在0、100、200、300、400、500ms位置。现在处理防抖部分：输入同样六个字符，但都不触发API调用，只是持续更新计时？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Type 'M'",
        "Type 'a'",
        "Type 'n'",
        "Type 'i'",
        "Type 'l'",
        "0",
        "600ms"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，六个输入事件用普通任务条表示，从0ms延续到600ms。然后关键是「Wait 500ms」这个等待阶段，用长条从600ms画到1100ms，最后才在1100ms处放一个milestone表示真正的API Call。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Wait 500ms",
        "API Call",
        "600",
        "1100ms",
        "milestone"
